caption.text:
Karna yang lain gak nanyain kenapa gw gak post, jadi gw post. It took a day for me to realize that this wasn't a dream. Everything that we tried, everything that we praticed, every blood tears and sweat, every second every thought im in so deep, every single thing that we gave for PCD, its all worth. From the first time we never looking for champion, for pride, or anything, we're just trying to entertain everyone, then its turn out to best dance, best flyer, best costume, and 1st winner, for me its just a bonus or maybe for us, but I want to tell you guys that we did, we really did it. 4 months for 10 minutes, and I'm proud to be a part of PCD squad this year, thanks to our captain and co captain @anasthaasia @alvinadbrt for bring us to victory haha. Gw personally juga mau minta maaf kalo tiap latihan gw suka lempar lempar krikil, percayalah itu bukan karna gw benci kalian atau gak respect dengan kalian, gw cuma suka diperhatiin ajah, sama emang dari lahir udah iseng. Maaf juga kalo waktu yang gue korbankan untuk latihan gak sebanyak waktu kalian, karna jadi artis tuh susah, dicari mulu dimana mana (?) Nothing could replace my memories with you guys, and I hope we have another time to make a good memories again. It would be incomplete if I wrote a message without a quote.
"If you feel no ones love you today, remember, no one loves you on the other day either"
By Dokter Boyke
